<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">@Caitlin - the basic message in the book is to ultimately re-map your thinking, being more exploratory/open-minded if you will. That said, you comment<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">@Caitlin - the basic message in the book is to ultimately re-map your thinking, being more exploratory/open-minded if you will. That said, you comment is representative of a closed mind. Maybe try NOT reading 210 pages in one sitting which IS representative of the book's message.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
